00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:32,280
Guru.

246
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,400
Ada satu hal di hati Haishi.

247
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:38,440
Kupikir-pikir lebih baik lapor
pada Guru agar lebih aman.

248
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:39,160
Katakan.

249
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:43,200
Hari ini saat bertugas, aku
bertemu Tuan Putri Yanling.

