00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:28,800
Anda baru kembali.

353
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,720
Kaisar sudah menolak menemui Anda.

354
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,560
Apa sungguh sesibuk itu?

355
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:34,760
Tak masalah.

356
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:36,760
Kita kunjungi di lain hari saja.

357
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:38,990
Aku juga sudah lama
tak kembali ke istana.

358
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:41,200
Sering jalan-jalan juga bagus.

359
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:46,680
Itu sepertinya bunga valeriana.

360
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:49,160
Kami tak kenal.

361
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:54,360
Bunga ini jarang ditemui
di ibu kota.

362
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:02,600
Jangan sampai Haishi dan Zhuoying
tahu masalah hari ini.

363
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:03,360
Baik.

364
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:07,480
Hanya saja hal ini cukup besar,
takutnya tak bisa ditutupi terlalu lama.

365
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:08,890
Usahakan menutupinya.

366
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,080
Baik.

367
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:15,840
Kaisar berusaha keras mengumpulkan
bunga valeriana dari selatan.

368
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:18,360
Dia sendiri malah mengurung diri,
tak mau temui siapa pun.

369
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,320
Menyia-nyiakan musim bunga ini.

370
00:22:21,520 --> 00:22:24,360
Mungkin ada masalah di hatinya,
jadi, tak bisa bersemangat.

371
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:27,600
Pergi ke sana.

372
00:22:27,760 --> 00:22:28,860
Bunga di sana sudah mekar.

373
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:29,920
Tuan Putri Yanling.

374
00:22:34,280 --> 00:22:34,840
Tuan Fang.

375
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:36,280
Fang Zhuoying.

376
00:22:37,280 --> 00:22:38,200
Tuan Putri hati-hati.

377
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,840
Tuan Putri Yanling di sini.

378
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:40,720
Kapal bergoyang.

379
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:41,840
Jangan sampai jatuh.

380
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:44,920
Kalian tak tahu bunga valeriana
sangat lembut.

381
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:48,160
Perlu sirami beberapa air di daun,
